<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>This could be a big help if you’re looking to incorporate Reels into your Instagram strategy this holiday shopping season.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>As part of its&nbsp;<a href="https://www.socialmediatoday.com/news/instagram-publishes-guides-help-brands-maximize-holiday-sales/632502/">new series of updated how-to guides</a>, Instagram has also launched a&nbsp;<a href="https://business.instagram.com/micro_site/url/?click_creative_path%5b0%5d=cta_button&amp;click_from_context_menu=true&amp;country=AU&amp;destination=https%3A%2F%2Fbusiness.instagram.com%2Fbusiness%2Furl%2F%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Ffacebook.com%252Fbusiness%252Ff%252F756084842380134%26cmsid%3D5094623593999772%26creative%3Dcta_button%26creative_detail%3D2022IGBBrandCampaignHowToGuidesConsolidatedPdfAPAC_ExploreTheGuide_Hero_Button%26create_type%3Ddownload%26destination_cms_id%26orig_http_referrer%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.google.com%252F%26search_session_id&amp;event_type=click&amp;last_nav_impression_id=1jxeyGZo5zNrgayRD&amp;max_percent_page_viewed=39&amp;max_viewport_height_px=944&amp;max_viewport_width_px=1866&amp;orig_http_referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2F&amp;orig_request_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fbusiness.instagram.com%2Finstagram-business-tools&amp;primary_cmsid=545445403973504&amp;primary_content_locale=en_GB&amp;region=apac&amp;scrolled=true&amp;session_id=0J4MM7drIiCNksPLw&amp;site=igb&amp;extra_data%5bcreative_detail%5d=2022IGBBrandCampaignHowToGuidesConsolidatedPdfAPAC_ExploreTheGuide_Hero_Button&amp;extra_data%5bcreate_type%5d=download&amp;extra_data%5bcreate_type_detail%5d=&amp;extra_data%5btarget%5d=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fbusiness%2Ff%2F756084842380134">new, 23-page overview</a>&nbsp;of how brands can use Instagram Reels for promotion and community building, which includes a range of key tips and notes on effective Reels usage.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>And there’s a heap of helpful pointers and notes here – first off, Instagram provides an overview of why you should consider Reels, and the key strengths of the format.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>‘The future of video storytelling on Instagram’. Pretty strong statement about where IG is headed – which further underlines why if you aren’t incorporating Reels into your Instagram marketing strategy yet, you’re likely already missing out on opportunities.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The guide also includes some helpful notes on Reels creation, including pointers on the ‘safe zones’ – i.e. where your content will and won’t be impacted by on-screen display overlays.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

